description:
In this exclusive online lesson, ArtistWorks Finger Style Guitar instructor, Martin Taylor, (http://bit.ly/2GAQTQK) demonstrates how to use your right hand to vary the volume and tone to make your playing more dynamic.

Access more lessons with Martin here: http://bit.ly/2GAQTQK
